    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Horse. You play as a wild horse with a freeform camera. It is you versus the world avoiding being captured. Natural disasters involving the elements, man, and gravity are your enemy. Preserve and increase your herd through your offspring, extending your lineage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/b0f507dd8dae56ad224fa57937afe086.poster.avif?t=1755708666\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/b0f507dd8dae56ad224fa57937afe086.webm?t=1755708666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/b0f507dd8dae56ad224fa57937afe086.mp4?t=1755708666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>You have no weapons, no rider, and a limited to no onscreen user interface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/8a90bda7f8596f016a591f1ca1c953a6.poster.avif?t=1755708666\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/8a90bda7f8596f016a591f1ca1c953a6.webm?t=1755708666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/8a90bda7f8596f016a591f1ca1c953a6.mp4?t=1755708666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a casual play mode for simply exploring to your heart's content to a full-blown single-player story mode that digs deep into this world with possible sinister intentions. It is up to you how you want to play and fantastically evolve!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
